{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"eb0288f960","title":"关于请上海会议各同志阅读薄一波发言稿的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"fe0e67b83e","index":0,"year":1959,"month":3,"day":26,"articleId":"eb0288f960"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d54ab0cc80","name":"薄一波","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji41","name":"毛泽东全集第41卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/41-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji41":{"comments":[{"id":"150bb5e5db","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"eb0288f960","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央1959年3月25日至4月1日在上海举行的政治局扩大会议。"},{"id":"8d103b4191","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"eb0288f960","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"薄一波，当时任中共中央政治局候补委员、国务院副总理兼国家经济委员会主任。"},{"id":"271a8f8538","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"eb0288f960","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"小平，即邓小平，当时任中共中央总书记、国务院副总理。"},{"id":"23fcf7ecf2","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"eb0288f960","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指薄一波准备在上海会议上作的关于1959年第一季度工业计划执行情况和第二季度安排的发言稿。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f2cf896e07","type":"title","text":"关于请上海会议“各同志阅读薄一波发言稿的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"eb0288f960"},{"id":"150bb5e5db","type":"paragraph","text":"少奇、小平可同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"eb0288f960"},{"id":"8d103b4191","type":"paragraph","text":"薄一波的发言印出来了，我正在看。今天上午，请将薄的发言印本，发给各同志阅读，先有一点印象，下午三时或四时开会，大家听一波宣读他的讲稿，就会「有丁获得一个较好的启发和理解了。须知有不少人是没有接触过这个问题的，心理状态各不一样。请照办为盼！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"eb0288f960"},{"id":"271a8f8538","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"eb02